<tr>

<td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700">JSON tool schema (9,948 chars)</td>

<td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700">2,631</td>

<td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700">3,306</td>

<td class="px-4 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700">+26%</td>

